{"tid":2130293,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【Apple】支那黑客宣佈破解到Security Enclave，請用緊A11代或之前裝置嘅人即刻換","createTime":"2020-07-29T06:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T07:59:52.000Z","uid":131691,"like":129,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"630021a90571ca2276778d75cd77af52d30e18de","tid":2130293,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:33:39.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://yalujailbreak.net/pangu-unpatchable-sep-bug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyalujailbreak.net%2Fpangu-unpatchable-sep-bug&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6anyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=ca3d05b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://yalujailbreak.net/pangu-unpatchable-sep-bug</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/axi0mX/status/1287010745826152454\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faxi0mX%2Fstatus%2F1287010745826152454&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6anyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=e39eb411\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faxi0mX%2Fstatus%2F1287010745826152454&h=84286c62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/axi0mX/status/1287010745826152454</a><br />\n<br />\nA11代裝置：iPhone X, 8, 8 Plus<br />\nA10：iPhone 7, 7 Plus, iPad 2018 6th gen, iPad 2019 7th gen, iPod touch 2019 7th gen<br />\nA9：iPhone 6S, 6S Plus, SE 1st gen, iPad 5th gen<br />\nA8：iPhone 6, 6 Plus, Apple TV 2015 4th gen, HomePod, iPad mini 4, iPod touch 2015 6th gen<br />\n<br />\nA12-13代嘅因爲仲未可以用Checkm8入所以而家「仲未破解到」（佢話）<br />\n<br />\nSecurity Enclave Processor基本上係儲存指模/FaceID/密碼嘅chip，亦都係限制「試密碼」唔可以極速係咁試嘅chip。<br />\n<br />\n================<br />\n<br />\n註：支那黑客team Pangu亦都係開發Checkm8嘅人，而香港警甴買嘅以色列Cellebrite其實就係包裝好支那Pangu/axi0mX發現嘅Checkm8，用嚟做入侵iPhone嘅方法。"},{"pid":"d9a313d2fe00c5d3e43ba7a5eaa7055513480b8c","tid":2130293,"uid":131691,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"Cellebrite用嘅Checkm8嘅詳細資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://pangu8.com/jailbreak/checkm8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpangu8.com%2Fjailbreak%2Fcheckm8%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6anyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=6e38b50a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pangu8.com/jailbreak/checkm8/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cellebrite.com/en/blog/a-practical-guide-to-checkm8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cellebrite.com%2Fen%2Fblog%2Fa-practical-guide-to-checkm8%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6anyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=5c6128cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cellebrite.com/en/blog/a-practical-guide-to-checkm8/</a>"},{"pid":"af5328f5a240ac4435e836da64b9f0b42673af02","tid":2130293,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5c40d1c55d973e50064c27f66ad59de90f17f8","tid":2130293,"uid":208011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:35:43.000Z","msg":"認真po推！"},{"pid":"90b6f9bd3d7fe645c327366c52220b8cfc27c630","tid":2130293,"uid":24345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要X打後"},{"pid":"2bdcf9a677b150eb9d7be75d122cb348d52a704d","tid":2130293,"uid":344625,"like":36,"dislike":9,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:37:24.000Z","msg":"自己hack自己再叫你比錢換機 高招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ec93ddc9b92e5f3a396bd0e545986d9ff53bc9","tid":2130293,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033648104faed56dbeb40ab5acf5e79dae6dcabf","tid":2130293,"uid":131691,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"90b6f9bd3d7fe645c327366c52220b8cfc27c630","tid":2130293,"uid":24345,"like":4,"di